Recent stock performance reflects growing market recognition. NSK **(#**[NPSKY](https://www.google.com/finance/quote/NPSKY:OTCMKTS)) has shown resilience and upward momentum through late 2025 into early 2026, with shares hitting new 1-year highs amid broader industrial recovery and automation plays.

